author=
description=00 = Raven Test
01 = MT Suppression
02 = Eliminate Informer
03 = Defend the Bridge
04 = Attack Rektena Installation
05 = Destroy Reserch Laboratory (UNUSED)
06 = Remove Disorder Units
07 = Capture Cargo
08 = Defuse Explosives
09 = Defend Arden River Lab
0A = Spaceport Escort
0B = Assist Malea Base
0C = Escort Train
0D = Guard Secret Information
0E = Ground-Based Attack
0F = Save Water-Generation Plant
10 = Assault Underwater Base
11 = Rescue Research Team
12 = Arden River Invasion
13 = Infiltrate Radar Base
14 = Destroy Radar Base
15 = Stop the Surface Weapon
16 = Guard HQ Rooftop
17 = Attack Research Team
18 = Destroy Containers
19 = Recover Stolen Files
1A = Escort Submarine
